                            <term xml:lang="bo" n="1">བསོད་ནམས་ཀྱི་ཚོགས།</term>
                            <term status="verified" xml:lang="Sa-Ltn" type="attestedOther">puṇyasaṃbhāra</term>
                            <note type="definition">
                                <p>The progressive increase of virtuous karma.
                                    One of the two factors that come together in creating momentum
                                    toward a practitioner’s spiritual awakening, the other being the
                                    accumulation or equipment of wisdom.</p>
                            </note>
